. Functional Requirements
A. Patient Management
Add/update/delete patient profiles

Link/unlink insurance

Maintain medical records (drugs, diagnoses, notes, etc.)

View historical data (reports, assessments)

B. Insurance Management
Create and associate insurance records with patients

Retrieve insurance data based on member or plan number

C. Medical Records
Store and retrieve:

Notes

Self-reports

Diagnoses

Assessment answers/questions

Drug prescriptions and their side effects

D. Doctor and Pharmacy Management
Associate doctors and pharmacies with patients

Query which drugs are linked to which doctors/pharmacies

E. Onboarding
Manage onboarding flow and responses

Store answers to onboarding questions
